    Cmo funcionan las opiniones y calificaciones de clientes

    Las opiniones de clientes, incluidas las valoraciones de productos ayudan a que los clientes conozcan ms acerca del producto y decidan si es el producto adecuado para ellos.

    Para calcular la valoracin global y el desglose porcentual por estrella, no utilizamos un promedio simple. En cambio, nuestro sistema considera cosas como la actualidad de la opinin y si el revisor compr el producto en Amazon. Tambin analiza las opiniones para verificar la confiabilidad.

    No se pudo cargar el archivo multimedia.
     We own a ton of fidget toys. We have a sensory story nearby that offers a tremendous selection of squishies, twisties, etc. However, I have never seen a rat fidget, so I ordered this one for my grandson.

    I was hoping it would move similarly to the popular fidget slugs, but since the pieces are shaped differently than the slug, it does not offer that flexibility of movement. They do provide tactile satisfaction, and since they come apart, you can also enjoy the experience of popping them back into place. I like the texture of the tail, but for me it's a little strange to be playing with a rat. (Yes, this is labeled "mouse," but its physical features like the long thick tail, pointy snout, and large teeth most resemble a rat.)

    I am hopeful that my five-year old grandson will enjoy dragging this around the house.
